bt es noch einen VVK im Foyer vor der Mensa.&nbsp;</p><p style="font-family:''Georgia'';font-size:12px;color:#000000 !important;background-color:#ededed;border:0;line-height:1.5em;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0;padding-top:3px;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0;vertical-align:top;word-wrap:break-word;">Wir freuen uns auf Ihr Kommen!</p><p style="font-family:''Georgia'';font-size:12px;color:#000000 !important;background-color:#ededed;border:0;line-height:1.5em;margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:1em;margin-left:0;padding-top:3px;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0;vertical-align:top;word-wrap:break-word;">Beste Grüße<br>Ihr Werkschauteam</p>\n                </div>\n            </td>\n        </tr>\n    </table>\n</div></td></tr></table>                    <table cellspacing="0" id="wysija_footer" align="center" style="background: none; background-color:transparent; border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0; margin-bottom: 0; margin-left: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0; padding-left: 0; padding-right: 0; padding-top: 0; width:600px;" width="600" cellpadding="0"><tr valign="top"><td id="wysija_header_content" style="margin-bottom: 0; margin-left: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0; padding-left: 0; padding-right: 0; padding-top: 0;" width="600"><div style="clear: both; margin-bottom: 0; margin-left: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-top: 0; padding: 0;"><table style="border-collapse: collapse; border-spacing: 0; margin: auto;" width="600"><tr>                        <td style="margin-bottom: 0; margin-left: 0; margin-right: 0; margin-top: 0; padding: 0;" width="600"><div   style="height:130px; max-height:130px;overflow:hidden;border:0;text-align:center;margin-top:0;margin-right:auto;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:auto;padding-top:0;padding-right:0;padding-bottom:0;padding-left:0;">                    <img class="wysija-image-center" src="http://werkschau.hs-augsburg.de/ss_13/w